r do, if his managerT\u2019aiid\nforemen and workers poured blame on him and flouted his j\norders? What could he do under such circumstances blit ap\npoint futile conferences and submit to a series of defeats?\nWhen Hoover was in private life\u2014when he had power,\nhe was efficient and successful. Jle made his companies pros\nperous. He earned a fortune.\nHe did not have to ask 9(5 Senators and 195 Congressmen\nwhat he could do\nIs not the Captain, oven of a political ship, entitled to the\nright of Leadership? In a storm, is he not entitled to au\nthority?\nIs he not entitled to Loyalty?\nThe passengers elected him.\nCorner Markham and Cross Streets\nPaisley-Lawson Drug Co.\n\u201cFriend of the Union Man\u201d\nTKe Gus Biass Co:\nATTEND THE SALE OF\nSample Dresses\nNow In Progress. $15 lo $129 Valins. Half Pi In-:\nStyles for livery Daytime or Keening Occasion\n47th Birthday Sale\nBrings a Golden\nOpportunity to Save\n\u2014for Working Folks!\nThe doors to Bark's Greatest Birthday Sa'\u2018<\nare open \\vi*i\u00bb-! Ami what a sale; W\\u\\\nprice* on nu-rehaiui'se lower the country\nover, uml es| eeially lower during this Bar\ngain Ffnst, what an opportunity is offered\nto working people who wish to he most f\nthrifty ami economical. \u00a31\nShoes\u2014Clothing\u2014Hats Every Department f\nAbounds in Real Birthday Values!\nYou cannot possibly believe that such st i\npendous values, that such low price* n g\nstylish, new, desirable merchandise preva.:! C\nuntil you COM I*. A.\\'l> SKK FOR YOU; Sj\n8KLK. I\nCome, Today or Tomorrow! Back\u2019s Greatest l\nOfferings in 47 Years Await You NOW!\nReport Made by Federal-State Employment Service.\nIJy W, A. Kooks her y.\nWith the publication of this re\nport there is now available for sta\ntistical purposes monthly figures\non the trend of employment in\nArkansas for the past year, show\ning the total number of wage earn\ners in selected industrial groups\ntogether with th/'ir total we kly\npay roll and average week!;